With this crystal, it is possible to customize the
appearance of the characters that appear in the
main game.

However, please note that only the appearance can
be changed, so there may be inconsistencies with
the dialogue and other aspects.

Also, please note that if you change the
character's gender or the presence of male
genitalia, it will not be compatible with the
character's specific H events (special intimate
scenes).

Welcome to the Secret Attic Room. In the Secret
Attic Room, you can customize the appearance of
the characters that appear in the main game.

There are also mannequins installed to check the
customized appearances.

Please be aware that changing the appearance may
cause inconsistencies in dialogue and
significantly alter the atmosphere of the game.
